(Greystone Capital Partners LLC is a mid-size real estate investment firm based in Miami, FL. The firm manages approximately $800 million in assets across office, retail, and multifamily properties. The principals have 15 years of experience in commercial real estate. The firm was involved in a dispute with a former limited partner in 2023 that was settled out of court. Sponsor net worth is reported at $45 million with liquidity of $8 million.) Tj
